# Participation Agreement Builder — local dev tooling & data.
# The whole tools/ dir stays local: the build script and the captured struct/
# data files contain REAL deal data (borrower names, loan #s, amounts), which
# must never be committed to this public repo. The committed templates
# (app/templates/participation_agreement_*.docx) hold only {{ placeholders }}.
